  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large Dutch oven over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the ground beef and cook until browned, breaking it up with a spoon as it cooks.",
    "Add the soaked and chopped red chillies, chilli powder, cumin, salt, and black pepper. Cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the canned diced tomatoes and bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and let the stew simmer for 30 minutes.",
    "Add the cooked kidney beans and smoked paprika (if using). Simmer for another 10 minutes.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with chopped fresh cilantro."
